User > Creates Blog Post [icon: file-text]
User > Comments on Blog Post [icon: message-square]
User > Likes Blog Post [icon: thumbs-up]
User > Bookmarks Blog Post [icon: bookmark]
User > Follows User [icon: user-plus]

Creates Blog Post > Blog [icon: file-text]
Comments on Blog Post > Comment [icon: message-square]
Likes Blog Post > Blog [icon: thumbs-up]
Bookmarks Blog Post > Blog [icon: bookmark]
Follows User > User [icon: user-plus]

Blog > Has Comments [icon: message-square]
Blog > Has Likes [icon: thumbs-up]
Blog > Has Bookmarks [icon: bookmark]
